{"type":"message","id":"f3f86b60","parentId":"5bf5bb14","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:32:31.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering installation permissions**\n\nI need to install something, and it seems like I might need elevated permissions for that. Before proceeding, I should ask for approval and provide the exact command, especially if the approval is still pending. So, my thought is to run the command `apt-get install caddy`, but I want to make sure I handle this correctly and get the necessary permission first. Let's clarify everything before moving forward!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"系统是 Debian 13，直接走官方 apt 安装最稳。我现在执行安装。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_TtRyTouyexxcsFE0vWzNlkuX","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"apt-get update && apt-get install -y caddy","workdir":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":1000,"timeout":120,"elevated":true,"ask":"on-miss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":426,"output":155,"cacheRead":36736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773797546942}}
{"type":"message","id":"6941ca33","parentId":"f3f86b60","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:32:31.537Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_TtRyTouyexxcsFE0vWzNlkuX","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"tool\": \"exec\",\n  \"error\": \"elevated is not available right now (runtime=direct).\\nFailing gates: allowFrom (tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider> / agents.list[].tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider>)\\nContext: provider=feishu session=agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\\nFix-it keys:\\n- tools.elevated.enabled\\n- tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider>\\n- agents.list[].tools.elevated.enabled\\n- agents.list[].tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider>\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","tool":"exec","error":"elevated is not available right now (runtime=direct).\nFailing gates: allowFrom (tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider> / agents.list[].tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider>)\nContext: provider=feishu session=agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\nFix-it keys:\n- tools.elevated.enabled\n- tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider>\n- agents.list[].tools.elevated.enabled\n- agents.list[].tools.elevated.allowFrom.<provider>"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773797551533}}
{"type":"message","id":"2742b079","parentId":"6941ca33","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:32:45.237Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Clarifying actions for response**\n\nI need to be careful about elevating my response levels. I could suggest commands or ask the user to run something, but that's not quite fitting. The user mentioned interpreting the config before, so it might be helpful to address that, too. They've also asked about installing Caddy, so I should certainly clarify the config in a concise manner. Keeping things brief is essential here!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这边能确认系统是 **Debian 13**，但我当前这个会话没有提权权限，没法直接替你执行 `apt-get install`。\n\n你在机器上跑这两句就行：\n\n```bash\nsudo apt-get update\nsudo apt-get install -y caddy\n```\n\n装完可以顺手验证：\n\n```bash\ncaddy version\nsystemctl status caddy --no-pager\n```\n\n顺带说下你上条那段配置：它是一个 **Caddyfile**，意思基本是：\n- 全局关闭 admin API\n- 关闭自动 HTTPS 重定向\n- 默认 SNI 设成 `127.0.0.1`\n- 内部证书和状态存到 `/data/caddy`\n- 对外监听 `https://127.0.0.1:8443`\n- 绑定 `0.0.0.0`，也就是所有网卡都能接\n- 用 `tls internal` 生成内部自签证书\n- 把请求反代到本机 `127.0.0.1:18789`\n\n有个点要提醒：**站点地址写的是 `https://127.0.0.1:8443`，但又 `bind 0.0.0.0`**。这意味着它虽然监听所有地址，但证书名和站点匹配目标是 `127.0.0.1`，拿别的 IP 去访问大概率会有证书不匹配警告。\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以直接帮你把这段配置整理成可用的 `Caddyfile`，顺便告诉你放哪、怎么启动。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":674,"output":478,"cacheRead":36736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37888,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773797551538}}
{"type":"message","id":"791b10f9","parentId":"2742b079","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:33:57.089Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54945ef2bcb4b36d27a711d7854\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 09:33 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54945ef2bcb4b36d27a711d7854]\nou_664eb5978d7a2e16127187d1c18827d3: 没问题 caddyfile 就是我给你的那个代码"}],"timestamp":1773797637086}}
{"type":"message","id":"2010f074","parentId":"791b10f9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T01:34:12.399Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 行，Caddyfile 就用你刚发的那份。\n\n但这边卡在一个很现实的问题：**我当前这个 Feishu 直连会话没有提权执行权限**，所以没法替你直接跑 `apt-get install`。你可以在机器上自己执行这两条：\n\n```bash\napt-get update\napt-get install -y caddy\n```\n\n装完后，把你的配置保存成比如 `/etc/caddy/Caddyfile`：\n\n```caddy\n{\n admin off\n auto_https disable_redirects\n default_sni 127.0.0.1\n skip_install_trust\n storage file_system {\n  root /data/caddy\n }\n}\n\nhttps://127.0.0.1:8443 {\n bind 0.0.0.0\n tls internal\n reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n}\n```\n\n然后执行：\n\n```bash\nsystemctl restart caddy\nsystemctl status caddy --no-pager\n```\n\n如果你要，我下一条可以直接给你一份 **Debian 13 从安装到启动的完整可复制命令清单**，包括创建 `/data/caddy`、写入 Caddyfile、重启服务和验证端口。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2728,"output":404,"cacheRead":36352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39484,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773797637088}}
