{"type":"message","id":"467e098c","parentId":"4dfefd68","timestamp":"2026-03-18T02:01:33.287Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Addressing the issue concisely**\n\nI need to provide a clear and concise answer. I should mention that I've found an issue and that I'm likely waiting for more information. There’s no need to bring up any tools for this. It’s important to keep things straightforward so that the user can easily understand the situation. Overall, maintaining clarity is key here!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 在看，问题已经定位到了，不是服务本身挂死，是 **Caddyfile 写法错了**。\n\n现在这份 `/etc/caddy/Caddyfile` 里有几个明显问题：\n\n1. `admin off` 被写进了 `:80 { ... }` 站点块里  \n   但它只能写在**最上面的全局配置块**里，所以报：\n   `unrecognized directive: admin`\n\n2. `storage filec_system` 拼错了  \n   应该是 `file_system`\n\n3. 文件底部还有个孤零零的 `$`  \n   这也是脏字符，最好删掉\n\n你要的配置，应该改成这样：\n\n```caddy\n{\n\tadmin off\n\tauto_https disable_redirects\n\tdefault_sni 127.0.0.1\n\tskip_install_trust\n\n\tstorage file_system {\n\t\troot /data/caddy\n\t}\n}\n\nhttps://127.0.0.1:8443 {\n\tbind 0.0.0.0\n\ttls internal\n\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n}\n```\n\n改完后执行：\n\n```bash\ncaddy validate --config /etc/caddy/Caddyfile --adapter caddyfile\nsystemctl restart caddy\nsystemctl status caddy --no-pager\n```\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接给你一份 **可直接覆盖 `/etc/caddy/Caddyfile` 的完整 shell 命令**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":42247,"output":369,"cacheRead":2560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45176,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773799279835}}
