{"type":"message","id":"5f275744","parentId":"a621f795","timestamp":"2026-03-18T04:20:10.233Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 因为我这边不是“不会”，是**权限不够**。\n\n准确说有两层限制：\n\n- 我能读取状态、看日志、定位问题  \n- 但我当前这个 **Feishu 直连会话没有提权执行能力**，所以像这些需要 root/systemd 的动作我不能直接替你跑：\n  - `apt-get install`\n  - `systemctl restart caddy`\n  - 改 `/etc/caddy/Caddyfile`\n\n之前我已经试过执行提权安装，系统直接拒了，报的是当前会话 **elevated is not available right now (runtime=direct)**。所以不是 Caddy 拒绝我，是这条会话本身不允许我拿 root 去动系统服务。\n\n### 我现在能做的\n我能继续替你：\n- 查日志\n- 看配置\n- 判断问题\n- 给你最短修复命令\n\n### 你那边需要亲自执行的\n如果你就是想把它拉起来，直接跑这组：\n\n```bash\nsudo tee /etc/caddy/Caddyfile >/dev/null <<'EOF'\n{\n\tadmin off\n\tauto_https disable_redirects\n\tdefault_sni 127.0.0.1\n\tskip_install_trust\n\n\tstorage file_system {\n\t\troot /data/caddy\n\t}\n}\n\nhttps://127.0.0.1:8443 {\n\tbind 0.0.0.0\n\ttls internal\n\treverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:18789\n}\nEOF\n\nsudo mkdir -p /data/caddy\nsudo chown -R caddy:caddy /data/caddy\n\nsudo caddy validate --config /etc/caddy/Caddyfile --adapter caddyfile\nsudo systemctl restart caddy\nsudo systemctl status caddy --no-pager -l\n```\n\n### 如果你愿意\n你把这几条命令的输出贴给我，我可以继续帮你盯到服务起来为止。  \n如果后面还起不来，我会继续顺着日志给你拆。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1001,"output":451,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47020,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773807590995}}
